**BBMP Grievances Dataset** (Bangalore Municipal Corporation)
- Source: OpenCity.in Urban Data Portal
- Size: 10,000+ grievance records
- Fields: Category, Location, Ward, Status, Timeline
- Citation: "BBMP Grievances Data," OpenCity - Urban Data Portal, Bangalore, India, 2024

